      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好的，我理解了。那具体流程怎么安排？是先有一个main分支的初始commit，然后开新分支做开发，最后合并回去吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "commit",
        "newbranch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是这个顺序。先在main上有一个初始提交，然后checkout到newbranch分支，在那边做一次提交，再切回main做merge。方向用LR横向展示。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "newbranch",
        "checkout",
        "merge",
        "LR"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，我来画一下：先commit，然后branch newbranch，checkout过去再commit，最后checkout main并merge newbranch。这样流程就闭环了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit",
        "branch newbranch",
        "checkout newbranch",
        "checkout main",
        "merge newbranch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚才说的顺序有点问题。应该是先在main上commit，然后branch newbranch，但不需要先checkout main再merge——不对，确实需要先checkout main才能merge。让我再确认一下：最终是要在main上完成merge newbranch，对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout main",
        "merge newbranch"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，您修正得很对。流程是：main上初始commit → 创建并切换到newbranch → newbranch上commit → 切回main → 在main上merge newbranch。这样newbranch的改动就合并到main了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "newbranch",
        "checkout",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "完美。另外我想确认下，这个图能清晰展示出分支点和合并点吗？特别是merge那个节点要有明显的合并视觉效果。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "branch point",
        "merge point"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没问题，Mermaid的gitGraph会自动处理。newbranch从main分出来的位置会有分支标记，最后的merge newbranch会显示为合并节点，两条线汇合成一条。整体横向LR布局，标题也按您要求设置好了。",
      "elements_involved": [
